    "gondola_customization_Azqz6w": {
      "type": "gondola-customization",
      "blocks": {
        "customization_q8zLpr": {
          "type": "customization",
          "settings": {
            "custom_image": "shopify://shop_images/gondola-structure-1.jpg",
            "customization_block_heading": "Solid Construction",
            "customization_block_desc": "<p>Gondola shelving is the backbone of retail display, widely used across the industry as a top choice for showcasing products. Our gondola shelving systems are built at the highest standards of quality, and offer various height and depth options, along with a diverse selection of shelves, cases, stands, and hooks. Additionally, it comes in a range of finishes and colors to suit any store's aesthetic.</p>"
          }
        },
        "customization_a8JcHe": {
          "type": "customization",
          "settings": {
            "custom_image": "shopify://shop_images/backing-choices.jpg",
            "customization_block_heading": "Panel Options",
            "customization_block_desc": "<p>From slat wall and plain panels, to perforated and metal grids, our custom gondola shelving back panel solutions are limitless. All backpanels are extremely sturdy and can hold hundreds of pounds of weight so you can rest assured your store is always in safe operations, while maintaining a beautiful aesthetic.</p>"
          }
        },
        "customization_wXBH4z": {
          "type": "customization",
          "settings": {
            "custom_image": "shopify://shop_images/gondola-shelving-choices.jpg",
            "customization_block_heading": "Shelving & Display Choices",
            "customization_block_desc": "<p>Our solid steel gondola shelves that can securely hold up to 500lbs of weight with ease. Dozens of alternative gondola shelving attachments are available, like display cases, magaize displays, baskets, slanted shelves, and many more for you to explore in our catalog.</p>"
          }
        },
        "customization_VheNTL": {
          "type": "customization",
          "settings": {
            "custom_image": "shopify://shop_images/Custom-Color-Chart.jpg",
            "customization_block_heading": "Custom Colors",
            "customization_block_desc": "<p>We understand the importance of branding and are dedicated to matching the branding of your company. Our color options range from standard White, Beige, Gray, and Black to specialty choices like Charcoal, Yellow, Nickel, Light Grey, Blue, Shiny Grey, Red, Pure White, and Hammertone. Let us help you create a cohesive and impactful brand presence.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
