        "customization_heading": "Gondola Shelving Customizations",
        "customization_block_sub": "<p>We've put together a selection of configuration options and features to give you an idea of the possibilities of our custom gondola shelving systems. These are just a few examples, and there are many more available. Contact us to discuss which options will best suit your needs.</p>"
